== Release ==
The film was released to theaters on March 1, 1973 by [[Paramont Pictures]] in the [[United States]]. It was released limitedly on February 22, 1973 in [[New York City]], and also released in [[West Germany]] on March 30, 1973, as well as August 11 in [[Sweden]], and August 25 in [[Japan]].

