== Trivia == 
* The animation style is different in [[Charlotte's Web 2: Wilbur's Great Adventure|Charlotte's Web 2]].
* Goof:When we first see Henry Fussy, he wears [[glasses]], but the next time we see him he doesn't wear glasses anymore. 
* Goof:At the beginning when Fern gives Wilber his first bath,the tub is full of bubbles.But when she rinses him off,all the bubbles disappear. Then, in the next shot the tub is full of bubbles again. 

